Package groups

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GL2_PrimeField
    A class that models the group of non-singular 2x2 matrices over a short integer prime field, implemented in the framework of the Group interface.
    GLn_PrimeField
    A class that models the group of non-singular square matrices over a short integer prime field, implemented in the framework of the Group interface.
    PGL2_PrimeField
    A class that models the group of non-singular projective 2x2 matrices over a short integer prime field, implemented in the framework of the Group interface.
    PGLn_PrimeField
    A class that models the group of non-singular projective square matrices over a short integer prime field, implemented in the framework of the Group interface.
    SymmetricGroup
    A class that models the group of permutations on the set {0, 1, ..., n-1}, for any int n>0, implemented in the framework of the Group interface.
